title: [Faeilythe's Fashions, Cloaks]
description: Diamond-paned glaes windows afford a view of the busy sunlit street, and the passersby occasionally stopping to gaze at the wares arranged here.  Garments have been arranged on a variety of displays, some draped with accessories for that extra flair.

Diamond-paned glaes windows afford a view of the quiet evening street, and the rare passersby stopping to gaze at the wares arranged here.  Garments have been arranged on a variety of displays, some draped with accessories for that extra flair.
